This layer acts as the bridge between your Core Logic and the browser's IndexedDB. By 2026 standards, we use Dexie.js because it provides an elegant, Promise-based wrapper around the clunky native IndexedDB API, ensuring ISO/IEC 25012 levels of data consistency and recoverability.

